  <description><![CDATA[<p>This traditional hotel has been updated to offer comfortable accommodation and modern amenities. It is picturesquely situated overlooking the old harbour of Desenzano in a central yet traffic-free area, 1 minute from the lakeside and 2 minutes' walk from the lake ferry. With cafés, pizzerias and restaurants all around, this is the ideal bed and breakfast location.</p>]]></description>
